	<td bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	<td class="subjectbar" height="20" style="font-size: 8pt;padding-left:10px;" width="100%">
		Miscellaneous (tiny) UI/Game Mechanics Niceties (for January Summit)

	</td>
	
		<td class="subjectbar" align=right style="padding:0px;padding-right:10px;">












		<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 border=0 id="io_bveteransm48894_table" 
		
			onClick="setId('48894');showLiMenu(this,'io_bveteransm48894','right',false);" 
			onDblClick="setId('48894');showLiMenu(this,'io_bveteransm48894','right',false);" 
			
		>
		<tr class=clickable>
			
				<td nowrap><a class=subjectbar_text style='font-size: 8pt;'>Options</a></td>
				
			<td>&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>
			<td><img src='/i/skins/default/button_options.gif' border=0 alt='Options' title='Options' width=11 height=28></td>
			<td>&nbsp;</td></tr>
		</table>
		
		</td></tr>
		
	<tr>
	
		<td class="msg_user_cell" width="150" valign=top>
		
			 









<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=51057'  class="auth_text"  style="font-weight:bold;" >	
<span style='color:#3333FF;'>Klonn_Darkbane</span></a>
			<br>
			
			<span style="font-size: 8pt;">
			Loremaster<br>
			
				Posts: 8421<br>
				
				Registered: 07-12-2004
				
			</span>
			


			
			<br>
			
				<img src="/i/p.gif" height=8 width=150 border=0 alt=""><br>
				
			<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=51057'>







<img src="http://www.eqbottomsup.org/sigs/klonn.gif" border=0 alt=""/></a><br>
			


			
			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=Veterans&message.id=48894#M48894">1</a> of 113
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 2841 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		
				background-color: #050A0E; 
				
				 background-image: none;
				 
				background-repeat: repeat-x;
				" 
			>
			<DIV>(no, these is not a "save EQ from impending doom" enhancements, not even a high-priority one, but if it can be passed to a nice Grumbok-type Dev who has some spare time and interest, it might get onto a back-burner somewhere)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>For lack of a better place to put them, I am starting this thread to collect tiny, nice-to-have, wishlist items to be passed to Devs. These items are so small that, IMO, they do not deserve their own threads. Hopefully some of them are so trivial that some dev might find a moment or two to implement them. In some cases, if a Dev is already in some piece of code for a different reason, perhaps one or two could be knocked off at the same time.</DIV>
<UL>
<LI>An on-screen indicator showing which camera (F9) is currently in effect. Sometimes it is hard to tell which camera is showing (especially when against a wall or FD). Even a simple number, 1-6, would be more than sufficient.</LI>
<LI>Another on-screen indicator showing if you have a suspended pet. Perhaps an icon in the Pet Window itself (yes, if you only have the single pet suspended, you could still have the window up, albeit empty - but with an indicator in the GUI, a custom UI could put that icon anywhere).</LI>
<LI>Arbitrary timer windows. We all time things, like spawns or other people's buffs. Some I know actually have kitchen timers sitting next to their PC. Why not just give us Timer windows, allowing us to put a comment at the top. Not sure they even need alarms or be countdown timers&nbsp;- a simple RESET button would work for me.</LI>
<LI>Since the advent of the Escape key closing windows, I use it A LOT. But I HATE the fact that it also untargets my current target as well. Can something be done about that?</LI>
<LI>Control-Tab is used to swap back and forth between targets. Alt-Tab is a window selector. Can you give us an option to turn off Alt-Tab? I know that Control-Tab can be remapped.</LI>
<LI>Why does Lev need to actually *bounce*? That just adds to lag.</LI>
<LI>Can I please have a "Self" button on the Bazaar search panel that automatically selects my race and class? Then, after pressing RESET (to clear all the other criteria), I can reset to ME quickly?</LI>
<LI>A "/camp login" command, similar to "/camp servers", so I can change accounts quickly.</LI>
<LI>Turn off attack when FD is cast, DON'T turn it off when I auto-stoop.</LI>
<LI>Tie "/assist on" and "/assist off" to the TOON, not to the entire client. Some of us play both melees and casters. With one setting for the account, it can be painful to switch between them.</LI></UL>
<P>Anybody got any others? I have no intention of presenting this list in a forum or group. I'd expect more to have it printed in my pocket and handing it to Grumbok (or copies to every dev I can find), carefully wrapped around some currency <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-happy.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></P>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							- There is no such thing as a train, only challenging pulls.<br>- Never get into a battle of wits with an unarmed man.<br>- MGB Max Extended True North at FV stone in 5 minutes! No level restrictions - HURRY!!!<br>- Try  <a href='/eq/search?advanced=true' class="searchbar_text">Searching</a>,  it's fun, fast and free!<br>- "I will nerf this" - <a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Veterans&message.id=119492#M119492" target="_BLANK">Absor</a
							</div>
								
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
		<td class="msg_date_cell" valign=bottom nowrap>
