<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Meriad wrote:<BR>My Wishlist for UI changes<BR><BR>- An official 'minimalist' skin for the EQUI.<BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE><BR>
<DIV>This made me think of one.&nbsp; I'd love to have&nbsp;a default&nbsp;layout.&nbsp; All my characters have the exact same layout of the windows.&nbsp; Yet, every time I start a new toon, I gotta rearrange everything to the way I like it.&nbsp; I'd love to be able to just type /layout default or something, and it would set that new toon to what I created as my default.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I'd like to be able to remap keys based on a character.&nbsp; I have an auto forage key set up, so every time I turn right, and the forage is available, it goes off.&nbsp; However, when playing my paladin, he doesn't need that.&nbsp; There's no way to change that without changing it for everyone.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
