		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<UL>
<LI>/AllowInspect ON OFF GROUP RAID ASK - would reduce those pesky inspections</LI>
<LI>BLOT OUT (like the badword filter) any item links in OOC and SHOUT (only OOC &amp; SHOUT) when used in PoK. Would make some things (like "FREE &lt;item&gt; to first tell"), but also eliminate the bigger PITA of people auctioning in OOC/SHOUT in PoK (and ONLY PoK). Do not make this optional so that the people doing the auctioning will get the idea.</LI>
<LI>Allow all 100 hotkeys to have their own keyboard keys assigned in OPTIONS. Then, to fire a given HotKey, you do not have to go to the right bank of hotkeys, then press the desired one - you could set up single hotkeys for very common actions.</LI>
<LI>/AllowExternalBuffs ON OFF RAID ASK - for buffs restricted to group, like Invis, Shrink, Grow</LI>
<LI>Allow up to five (?) TARGETLOCKS. Target something, specify /TARGETLOCK &lt;number&gt;. Now I can make a hotkey (or assign a key) to retarget that specific thing. For example, on a raid, target the MA, specify /TARGETLOCK 1, then press "M" (or whatever) to retarget that toon, as long as he is in zone.</LI>
<LI>We definitely need BOLD/ITALIC/UNDERLINE in all say/tell/gsay/rsay/ooc/shout</LI>
<LI>Allow tells from Friends/Non-Friends to be filtered to different chat windows (and different color options might be nice, too)</LI>
<LI>Put a little control button on chat windows to jump to the bollom. Often, it is dillicult to get to the complete bottom if the window is relatively small and it has a lot of text in it. Might be nice if the button had a visual cue (constantly pressed?) that shows that the window is currently tailing the chat.</LI></UL>
